HEADWORD: Dedecorate
<hw>De*dec"o*rate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>dedecoratus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>dedecorare</ets> to disgrace. See
<er>Decorate</er>.]</ety> <def>To bring to shame; to disgrace.</def>
